
<center><h1>Welcome to Unicoin,
    <%= current_user.name.capitalize %>!</h1>
    <h2>Your journey to paying for college starts here.</h2>
</center>

<h3>STEP 1</h3>
Sign up for your FSA ID.

<h3>STEP 2</h3>
Fill out our simplified FAFSA application.

  <h2><%= link_to 'Start a new 2017-2018 FAFSA', new_user_response_path if current_user.user_responses.count == 0 %></h2>
  <h2><%= link_to 'Continue FAFSA', brand_new_path if current_user.user_responses.count > 0 %></h2>
  <h2><%= link_to 'Update a saved FAFSA', user_responses_path if current_user.user_responses.count > 0 %></h2>

<h3>STEP 3</h3>
Upload pictures of your tax returns and your parents tax returns.
  <%= render 'users/image_upload', user: current_user %>

<h4>STEP 4</h4>
Verify that all of the information on your completed FAFSA is accurate.

<h4>STEP 5</h4>
Submit your completed FAFSA!
